    <p><b>About</b></p>
    <p>Gaigaile (Gǎi gǎi lè) is the ultimate online resource for Chinese students looking to apply to overseas universities. Applying to schools can seem daunting, but it’s definitely not impossible. In fact, at Gaigaile, we think that with the right resources, everyone can be successful in school applications. Our free online resources will help you better understand the application process, select your target schools, and prepare you for success abroad, while our editing platform will help you prepare and improve all of the necessary documentation.</p>
    <p><b>Our Editing Platform</b></p>
    <p>Our easy-to-use platform connects Chinese students with qualified editors in the United States that provide professional editing and content recommendations for application essays and personal statements. Gaigaile editors are all native English speakers educated at the top universities in the United States. Having gone through the application process themselves, they are knowledgeable of all key criteria schools are looking for and are excited to help you succeed.</p>

